### File HTTP tests

@base=http://localhost:8000
@json=application/json
@token=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Upload file
POST {{base}}/api/files
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"

File content here
--boundary--

### List files
GET {{base}}/api/files
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get file details
GET {{base}}/api/files/1
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Download file
GET {{base}}/api/files/1/download
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update file
PUT {{base}}/api/files/1
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "name": "renamed.txt"
}

### Delete file
DELETE {{base}}/api/files/1
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Bulk delete
POST {{base}}/api/files/bulk-delete
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "file_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

